                    <h3 class="mb-0"><i class="fas fa-lock"></i> Symmetric Encryption</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>Symmetric encryption uses the same key for both encryption and decryption. Modern algorithms like AES (Advanced Encryption Standard) provide strong security for sensitive data.</p>
                    <div class="text-center mt-4">
                        <div class="cipher-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-key"></i> ⟶ <i class="fas fa-lock"></i> ⟶ <i class="fas fa-key"></i>
