                    <h3 class="mb-0"><i class="fas fa-key"></i> Asymmetric Encryption</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>Asymmetric encryption uses a pair of keys: public and private. RSA and ECC algorithms enable secure communications without sharing secret keys, powering HTTPS and digital signatures.</p>
                    <div class="text-center mt-4">
                        <div class="cipher-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-unlock"></i> ⟶ <i class="fas fa-lock"></i> ⟶ <i class="fas fa-key"></i>
